        @{fg shine}ExecuteCommand@{fg text}

@{b}Function:@{ub}       Execute a DOS command.
@{b}Syntax:@{ub}         COMMAND/K,ASK/S
@{b}Result:@{ub}         0  - Ok.

@{b}Options:@{ub}        COMMAND:        The DOS command you want to execute
